OL,3,CPalestinian filmmaker wins LGBTQ+ film
OL,4,Cfestival
OL,6,FA filmmaker from Palestine has won at
OL,7,Fthe world's biggest LGBTQ+ fest
OL,8,Ffestival.
OL,10,FDima Hamdan won the prestigious award
OL,11,Ffor her short film, Blood Like Water.
OL,12,FShe said she was, "deeply honoured to
OL,13,Freceive the 2024 Iris Film Prize".
OL,15,FThe Berlin-based journalist's previous
OL,16,Fshort film, The Bomb, won her 'Best
OL,17,FFemale Director' at the Ayodhya Film
OL,18,FFestival in India.
