OL,3,CPalestinian filmmaker wins LGBTQ+ film
OL,4,Cfestival
OL,6,FThe organisers of the six-day event
OL,7,Fsay it is a celebration of LGBTQ+
OL,8,Ffilms and this year attracted 11,000
OL,9,Fadmissions.
OL,11,FIts director, Berwyn Rowlands, said,
OL,12,F"I'm very proud that Iris is able to
OL,13,Fshare stories not nescessarily covered
OL,14,Fby the mainstream. This years
OL,15,Ffilmmakers have focused on the more
OL,16,Fserious aspects of LGBTQ+ life.
OL,17,FAlthough many are dark, there is still
OL,18,Fhope".
